                    <!-- <img src="/images/metadatapage-showcase.png" alt="A streak" class="ui fluid image"> -->
                </div>
                <div class="six wide column">
                    <h3 class="ui center aligned header">Learn about yourself through your data. 
                        Want to see how your mood changes during different times of the year? You got it.
                        Curious if your thoughts have been more positive since you started that yoga class? We can help with that. 
                        Wondering what was on your mind a year ago today? Find out without reading a word.
                        Everything is displayed in the form of beautiful, minimalist charts and graphs. 
                    </h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row"><div class="spacer"></div></div>
            <div class="row">
